Gitweb Lite

  (Beta release)
  gitweb.cgi clone. Serve git repository.

Features

  This is gitweb.cgi clone, and has the more following features.

  - gitweblite is written by Perl and Mojolicious
  - You can run "gitweblite.pl" very easily,
    even if "apache" is not installed
  - You can set Multiple project roots

Operation

  Start
  
    hypnotoad script/gitweblite
  
  Stop
  
    hypnotoad  --stop

NOTE

  I will make gitweblite a application which has no dependency,
  but in beta relase, you need the following module to run gitweblite
  
    Mojolicious
    Validator::Custom

  And now some feature is lacked.
